<div class="bg-indigo-50 dark:bg-indigo-900/10 rounded-2xl p-6 mb-8 border border-indigo-100 dark:border-indigo-800/30">
  <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
    <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-indigo-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold shadow-lg shadow-indigo-200 dark:shadow-none">
      QA
    </div>
    <div>
      <h3 class="font-bold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">有技术问题？</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400">在问答区提问，获取解答</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <p class="text-sm text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
