      <span>详细的问题描述</span>
    </div>
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">
      <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-indigo-500"></span>
      <span>代码片段或截图</span>
    </div>
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">
      <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-indigo-500"></span>
      <span>尝试过的解决方案</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
